{"tid":2098952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習清洗公安系統 孟建柱「病重住院」 重兵把守如囚禁 料成徐才厚第二","createTime":"2020-07-08T01:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:57:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8589f028498d3cbc1e75a9a928d7115ac5a9e1","tid":2098952,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:11:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200708/R3OV6H7XPRC4OVW67QKQAGWANU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200708%2FR3OV6H7XPRC4OVW67QKQAGWANU%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=9029d466\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200708%2FR3OV6H7XPRC4OVW67QKQAGWANU%2F&h=184c82f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200708/R3OV6H7XPRC4OVW67QKQAGWANU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n習清洗公安系統 孟建柱「病重住院」<br />\n重兵把守如囚禁 料成徐才厚第二<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WkQXoFSBhkgB6DsO50Lo-47q6L8=/190x130/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4V7QHFM7Z4ZTVXTEOFIREXWJFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWkQXoFSBhkgB6DsO50Lo-47q6L8%3D%2F190x130%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4V7QHFM7Z4ZTVXTEOFIREXWJFY.jpg&h=5d74586b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共前政治局委員、公安部長孟建柱傳被當局立案調查，目前因病住院，有重兵把守。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國華文媒體明鏡新聞網創辦人何頻透露，中共公安部高層近期一系列人事異動，為習近平清洗「周永康餘黨」、削平公安部長期存在的「山頭文化」動作之一。前中央政治局委員、政法委書記孟建柱已被當局立案調查，目前「病重住院」，由解放軍重兵把守自由受限，可能重演當年軍委副主席徐才厚被關在醫院審查至死一事。何認為習的連番動作，反映出「重整公安部」的意圖。<br />\n<br />\n何頻昨在明鏡新聞節目「點點今天事<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n證明習對公安部的清洗還未完結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N2Q0NQNX5rVb2BAIfWlXjsRkrTI=/190x136/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W24WL253CCATIJLHPZ3R7PIIKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN2Q0NQNX5rVb2BAIfWlXjsRkrTI%3D%2F190x136%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW24WL253CCATIJLHPZ3R7PIIKM.jpg&h=d372c26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孟建柱是由周永康（右）一手提拔上位。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oMH5IfIH_vIbu8fRevdjXBvu1zw=/190x132/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3OQCJVSN4GS7EMCGG5PXTMYEJY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoMH5IfIH_vIbu8fRevdjXBvu1zw%3D%2F190x132%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3OQCJVSN4GS7EMCGG5PXTMYEJY.gif&h=bea6c671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公安部近期屢現人事異動，或涉中共內部權鬥黑幕。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周永康提拔 後倒戈<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：權鬥重地 公安部長難有好下場<br />\n<br />\n何頻指，若說公安部副部長孟慶豐日前被去職是年屆63歲，到副部級退休之齡，那另一位61歲的副部級黨委委員、反恐專員劉躍進離職，則大有袜坤；「當局沒通報劉去職原因，但大家都知道，劉耀進是孟建柱的人。」何認為這些動作都明顯劍指孟建柱。至於孟建柱目前的情況，何頻指外傳孟已被中共抓捕的消息不實，「我從多方了解到，孟目前正在醫院住院，一方面他的身體確實不好，另一方面，以住院養病的名義躲避當局審查，是中共不少高官的慣用手段」。<br />\n<br />\n何頻未透露孟建柱身處哪間醫院，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n何暗示看守孟的重兵來自解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心腹孫力軍已落馬<br />\n<br />\n目前不清楚習近平為何要拿下孟建柱。除當局反覆強調，公安部要「切實從思想上、政治上、組織上、作風上肅清周永康流毒影響」之外，海外有報道指，孟助習拿下周永康、接掌公安部後，大權在握「不懂敬畏」，<br />\n。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1a53598ddabe3ae83016edec3c37cdd6609bc611","tid":2098952,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"aac0aef94bb858fed34acb222fe2af5f171b662f","tid":2098952,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"68fa3d0340b3e29e5e52f051a6d1b16d6220f2d8","tid":2098952,"uid":66378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"崇禎：「朕非亡國之君，乃諸臣誤朕」"},{"pid":"13d4bf8c34d063536e303633e8681219dc27c9e8","tid":2098952,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"郭文貴講, 信不信由你:<br />\n<br />\n孟建柱喜歡後門&hellip;王芳幾次住院都是因為&hellip;這些事被雷洋知道，所以必死&hellip;"}]}